Title: Congratulating Angelina McKane upon the occasion of capturing the Girls 50-yard Freestyle title at the NYSPHSAA Girls Swimming and Diving Championship on November 19, 2022
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION congratulating Angelina McKane upon the occasion of capturing both the Girls 50-yard Freestyle and the Girls 100-yard Butterfly title at the NYSPHSAA Girls Swimming and Diving Championship on November 19, 2022
